de.esoco.lib.expression.function

Class Group<I>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.obrel.core.RelatedObject
      • de.esoco.lib.expression.function.AbstractFunction<I,I>
        • de.esoco.lib.expression.function.Group<I>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Function<I,I>, Relatable

    public class Group<I>
extends AbstractFunction<I,I>
    A function implementation that groups an arbitrary number of consumers and applies all of them successively to input values in the same order in which they are added to the group. The list of the consumers in a group can be queried with getMembers().
